condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Comprehensive Record Keeping System | Description :The Borrower shall ensure that a comprehensive record keepingsystem for the PCU has been established in a manner satisfactory to the Bank by not later than three (3) months after the EffectiveDate. | Due Date :30-Nov-2016

Finance Agreement :Computerized Accounting System | Description :The Borrower shall acquire and install, not later than three (3)months after the Effective Date, and thereafter maintain, a computerized accounting system acceptable to the Bank, for the Project.| Due Date :31-Oct-2016

Finance Agreement :Environmental and Social Specialist | Description :The Project Coordination Unit shall employ, not later thansix (6) months after the Effective Date and thereafter maintain at all times during Project implementation, an environmental andsocial specialist whose qualifications, experience and terms of reference shall be acceptable to the Bank. | Due Date :31-Jan-2017

Finance Agreement :External Auditor | Description :The Borrower shall employ, not later than four (4) months after the EffectiveDate, the external auditor in accordance with Section III of Schedule 2 of the Loan Agreement and pursuant to terms of referencesatisfactory to the Bank. | Due Date :30-Nov-2016

Finance Agreement :National Office for Employment Accountant | Description :The National Office for Employment shall, not laterthan three (3) months after the Effective Date, employ and thereafter maintain at all times during Project implementation, anaccountant whose qualifications, experience, and terms of reference shall be acceptable to the Bank. | Due Date :31-Oct-2016

Finance Agreement :Procurement Training | Description :The Borrower shall ensure that a procurement training has been provided toappropriate staff responsible for Project implementation by not later than two (2) months after the Effective Date. | Due Date:30-Sep-2016

Finance Agreement :Steering Committee | Description :The Borrower shall establish, not later than one (1) month after the EffectiveDate, and thereafter maintain, throughout the Project implementation period with composition, mandate, and resources satisfactoryto the Bank, a steering committee, to be chaired by the Minister of MFPIJ or a designate and comprised of representatives of keyministries, agencies, the private sector and civil society. | Due Date :31-Aug-2016

Finance Agreement :Technical Auditors | Description :The Borrower shall no later than six (6) months after the Effective Date,recruit technical auditors with qualifications, experience, and terms of reference satisfactory to the Bank and in accordance withthe provisions of Section III of Schedule 2 of the Loan agreement, to conduct yearly external evaluations of the Performance BasedContracts (PBCs). | Due Date :31-Jan-2017
